

//English (Original)

Privacy Policy

We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. 
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website. 
By using our site, you consent to our use of cookies and data collection as outlined in this policy. 
Please read the following information carefully to understand our views and practices regarding your personal data and how we will treat it.


//Indonesian (Translation)
Kebijakan Privasi

Kami sangat menghargai privasi Anda dan berkomitmen untuk melindungi data pribadi Anda. 
Kebijakan Privasi ini menjelaskan bagaimana kami mengumpulkan, menggunakan, dan melindungi informasi pribadi Anda saat Anda mengakses situs web kami.
Dengan menggunakan situs kami, Anda menyetujui penggunaan cookie dan pengumpulan data sebagaimana dijelaskan dalam kebijakan ini. 
Harap baca informasi berikut dengan teliti untuk memahami pandangan dan praktik kami mengenai data pribadi Anda serta bagaimana kami akan menanganinya.



//Key Points in Translation

Tone & Formality: 
The translation maintains a formal and professional tone, which is crucial for privacy-related content on websites.

Terminology:
"Personal Data" is translated to "data pribadi", which directly conveys the intended meaning in the context of privacy.
"Cookies" remains the same in both languages, as it is a commonly understood term in tech and website contexts.

Structure & Clarity: 
The sentence structure is kept simple yet clear, ensuring that the message is easily digestible for Indonesian users.

Cultural Adaptation: 
Terms like "consent" and "understand" are retained in their formal, legal context, as this ensures the message aligns with Indonesian data protection norms and policies.

